items.typeLine: Necromancer's Corvine Charm of the Trickster
explicitMods: Your Offerings have 30% increased Effect on you
5% chance to Recover 10% of Mana when you use a Skill
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Charm Socket on the Wildwood Primalist Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.

items.name: Militant Faith
explicitMods:
Carved to glorify 4029 new faithful converted by High Templar Avarius
Passives in radius are Conquered by the Templars
4% reduced Elemental Ailment Duration on you per 10 Devotion
3% increased Defences from Equipped Shield per 10 Devotion
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: They believed themselves the utmost faithful, but that conviction became oppression.

items.name: Careful Planning
explicitMods: Intelligence from Passives in Radius is Transformed to Dexterity
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: "Greatly outnumbered, Deshret dressed her personal guard
in identical garb. When the Empire rode north, Deshret and
her guard took turns revealing themselves, creating the illusion
of speed beyond the capabilities of even the Virtue Gems."
